    "longBusinessSummary": "Vietnam National Seed Group Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the research, development, and sale of crop seeds in Vietnam. The company offers crop seeds, such as rice, corn, and vegetable seeds; organic farm products, such as organic rice and fresh vegetables; and agricultural materials comprising herbicide maizine, fungicide foraxyl, and foliar fertilizer supermes, as well as various agricultural services. It also provides logistic services; produces and trades all kinds of plant varieties; researching, producing, trading and exporting of plant varieties and agricultural products; high-quality melons and vegetables for domestic consumption and export; researching, applying, training and transferring high-tech agricultural technical services; wholesale and retail agency; agricultural and forestry machinery; food and beverage processing; and repair, maintenance and installation of machinery and equipment, as well as involved in wholesale of rice, wheat, other cereals and flours. Vietnam National Seed Group Joint Stock Company was founded in 1968 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam. Vietnam National Seed Group Joint Stock Company is a subsidiary of The Pan Group Joint Stock Company.",
